uint32_t vpsissCalCmplxIoLaneCfg::position

Specify if this lane is to be used, if so, on which position. 0x0 - Not used / disabled lane 0x1 - Position 1 0x2 - Position 2 0x3 - Position 3 0x4 - Position 4 0x5 - Position 5
